Gentlemen Prefer Blondes
plot_summary: TEST PLOT SUMMARY. Lorelei Lee, a blonde flapper from Arkansas, keeps a diary of her adventures as she manipulates wealthy men for money and gifts. Sponsored by button manufacturer Gus Eisman, she travels to Paris with her friend Dorothy, where she continues scheming to marry rich men while collecting jewelry and diamonds. Through calculated naivety and charm, she ultimately secures a wealthy husband, achieving her goal of financial security through marriage.
